  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age &gt;18 years

          -  Expected duration of infusion therapy by short peripheral intravenous catheters &gt;7
             days

          -  Give written informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  The peripheral venous catheter was inserted in emergency room or in emergency
             circumstances

          -  Bloodstream infection

          -  Had a peripheral venous catheter already in situ at the baseline

          -  Altered mental state
      </textblock>
